The,Accelerite,LaaS,API,allows,developers,to,access,the,location,information,of,millions,of,mobile,devices,including,basic,phones,without,GPS,or,data,connectivity,in,order,to,create,applications,that,are,location,aware,Accelerite,LaaS,Location,as,a,Service,is,a,service,for,creating,context,aware,business,applications,that,use,the,locations,of,customers,employees,and,assets